to create a user account into clowder.

example to run:
1) create admin account 
docker run --rm -it -e "PASSWORD=youpassword" -e "EMAIL_ADDRESS=youremailaddress" -e "ADMIN=true" --name create-useraccount browndog/create-useraccount

2) create normal user account
docker run --rm -it -e "PASSWORD=yourpassword" -e "EMAIL_ADDRESS=youremailaddress" --name create-useraccount browndog/create-useraccount
